title: United Kingdom Imports of Miscellaneous Edible Prepared
description: Imports of Miscellaneous Edible Prepared in the United Kingdom decreased to 282.88 GBP Million in September from 289.33 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Miscellaneous Edible Prepared in the United Kingdom averaged 166.68 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 322.15 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 52.17 GBP Million in January of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Miscellaneous Edible Prepared.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
